# Dashboard REST API Summary

This documentation details the Dashboard REST API, which allows developers to retrieve data displayed on Amplitude dashboard graphs in JSON format. The API provides endpoints for event segmentation, funnel analysis, retention analysis, user activity, and more, with support for filtering, segmentation, and grouping.

